    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Candlaron the Sculptor is one of Kyonin\u2019s most storied and honored wizards. While his final fate is unknown, his greatest creations, the aiudara, remain behind as a legacy of his power\u2014as do other potent items, such as the *Guiding Star Orb*, a navigational traveling aid that the heroic wizard often relied upon when venturing into an unexplored part of the world.",
